README
============================================================================================

To use the Slider component , please enter the following tag in your HTML :

<div id="slider -storm">
</div>

And in their imports of js and css sure the following features contained in the project were imported :

  <! - PREMISES JS & CSS ​​->
  <script src="js/jquery- 1.10.2.js"></script>
  <script src="js/jquery- ui.js"></script>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/jquery-ui.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/jquery-style.css">

  <! - STORM CSS & JS ->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/slider-storm.css">
  <script src="js/storm-slider.js"> </script>

